Happy Father’s Day to my amazing dad. I am so thankful to have such a great leader, who has taught me so much in business and how to be a great businessman. He is one of the best people I know. I am so thankful to have been able to be fortunate enough to have had him throughout my life and to have taught me so much.. I’m very thankful that we are able to work along side each other and with each other on a day-to-day basis and that we get to see each other often with our busy lives. I will always remember the times that were special to me through my football, hunting, and work successes as he has had a major Intrachol part of my life for those successes in one way or another. I will always remember no matter how busy he was. He always made time for the things that were most important in my life and never missed a football game in Little League, middle school, high school, and college. He was always there cheering for me as my number one fan and still is… Thank you dad for always being there for me and for caring so much about our families life and sacrificing so much to make everything work the way that it has. I love you very much ❤️❤️❤️ #happy #fathersday #father #bond #love #God1st
